{"word":"G1097 - γινώσκω - ginṓskō - ghin-oce'-ko - Allow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γινώσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ginṓskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ghin-oce'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Allow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அறிந்திரு, உணர்ந்திரு, தெரிந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":"to learn to know, come to know, get a knowledge of"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of a primary verb; to &ldquo;know&rdquo; (absolutely), in a great variety of applications and with many implications (as shown at left, with others not thus clearly expressed): - allow, be aware (of), feel, (have) known (-ledge), perceive, be resolved, can speak, be sure, understand.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1097/1097\">G1097</a>, <a href=\"#/G1106/1106\">G1106</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107/1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108/1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110/1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176/176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1921/1921\">G1921</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922/1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607/2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267/4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268/4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774/4774\">G4774</a>"}]}